0.code:
s = 'KxHP'
K = 25
ans = ''
for i, c in enumerate(s):
    dif = ord('z') - ord(c) + 1
    dif %= 26
    if i == len(s) - 1:
        K %= 26
        if ord(c) + K > ord('z'):
            K -= 26
        ans += chr(ord(c) + K)
    elif dif <= K:
        ans += 'a'
        K -= dif
    else:
        ans += c
print(ans)

        K -= dif
    else:
        ans += c
print(ans)
